1
00:00:07,006 --> 00:00:10,009
(Yao) I decided to support Koharu-chan.

2
00:00:10,009 --> 00:00:12,512
(Kurosaki) I couldn't control my jealousy towards Yuio-kun.

3
00:00:12,512 --> 00:00:17,016
The closer the two of us become, the more our hearts become agitated.

4
00:00:17,016 --> 00:00:19,519
(Koharu) I'm glad you told me your true feelings.

5
00:00:19,519 --> 00:00:21,521
Let's aim for a lover that we can communicate with.

6
00:00:21,521 --> 00:00:24,023
It means I love you!

7
00:00:24,023 --> 00:00:26,025
sorry.

8
00:00:26,025 --> 00:00:30,029
I have always hated you, both before and now.

9
00:00:30,029 --> 00:00:34,534
So from now on, I'm going to destroy something important to you.

10
00:00:34,534 --> 00:00:37,036
I hope you make it in time.

11
00:00:37,036 --> 00:00:38,538
big brother.

12
00:00:38,538 --> 00:00:50,049
♬～

13
00:00:50,049 --> 00:00:52,552
Yuio-san...

14
00:00:52,552 --> 00:00:55,555
I've always hated him➡

15
00:00:55,555 --> 00:01:00,555
I want to hurt him and make him unhappy.

16
00:01:02,061 --> 00:01:04,998
You're really stupid, Koharu-chan.

17
00:01:04,998 --> 00:01:08,501
You've been fooled by me this whole time.

18
00:01:08,501 --> 00:01:10,003
picture…?

19
00:01:10,003 --> 00:01:16,009
The reason why I started working part-time with Shirase and the reason why I was kind to Koharu-chan➡

20
00:01:16,009 --> 00:01:20,009
Because I wanted to steal something important from him.

21
00:01:23,016 --> 00:01:29,022
But if I got dumped and can't take it back, then it's okay.

22
00:01:29,022 --> 00:01:36,029
♬～

23
00:01:36,029 --> 00:01:41,534
So... Yuo-san I've seen so far➡

24
00:01:41,534 --> 00:01:44,534
Does that mean it was all a lie?

25
00:01:49,542 --> 00:01:54,042
That's right, it's definitely a lie.

26
00:01:56,549 --> 00:01:58,549
It's not a lie...

27
00:02:00,053 --> 00:02:02,989
It's not a lie! What are you talking about?

28
00:02:02,989 --> 00:02:05,492
It's true that Yuo-san is foul-mouthed and forceful➡

29
00:02:05,492 --> 00:02:08,495
Maybe he was trying to take advantage of me.

30
00:02:08,495 --> 00:02:11,498
But for that purpose, I have a part-time job and a private tutor➡

31
00:02:11,498 --> 00:02:14,000
Was it necessary to work so hard?

32
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:18,505
Well... that's because it's more convenient to increase your likeability...

33
00:02:18,505 --> 00:02:20,006
no!

34
00:02:20,006 --> 00:02:23,009
Yuio-san is a serious and hard-working person.

35
00:02:23,009 --> 00:02:26,012
teeth? On what basis do you treat me like a good person?

36
00:02:26,012 --> 00:02:31,017
I know that Yuo-san is a kind person.

37
00:02:31,017 --> 00:02:33,520
No matter what Yuo says about me➡

38
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:37,524
I believe that Yuo-san is a kind person!

39
00:02:37,524 --> 00:02:41,524
Then you said something like you understood me again...

40
00:02:44,030 --> 00:02:47,534
Ah, shit... something went wrong...

41
00:02:47,534 --> 00:02:49,534
What is it really...

42
00:02:51,037 --> 00:02:53,540
What about Koharu-chan➡

43
00:02:53,540 --> 00:02:57,040
It was just a pawn to make him suffer.

44
00:02:59,546 --> 00:03:04,946
But I already love you...

45
00:03:10,990 --> 00:03:14,994
Even if you look at my lame and disgusting side➡

46
00:03:14,994 --> 00:03:17,494
You made me laugh when I was worried.

47
00:03:20,500 --> 00:03:24,000
Because he said it was wonderful.

48
00:03:30,009 --> 00:03:32,509
To Koharu-chan...

49
00:03:35,014 --> 00:03:38,014
I wanted to be loved.

50
00:03:40,019 --> 00:03:42,021
Yuio-san...

51
00:03:42,021 --> 00:03:53,533
♬～

52
00:03:53,533 --> 00:03:55,533
sorry.

53
00:03:57,537 --> 00:04:00,037
I'm really sorry.

54
00:04:02,041 --> 00:04:03,977
it's okay.

55
00:04:03,977 --> 00:04:06,980
but….

56
00:04:06,980 --> 00:04:10,980
Why did you want to make Kurosaki-san unhappy?

57
00:04:12,986 --> 00:04:15,488
Me…➡

58
00:04:15,488 --> 00:04:19,993
Even if I can forgive what was done to me➡

59
00:04:19,993 --> 00:04:23,993
I absolutely don't want Kurosaki-san to get hurt.

60
00:04:25,498 --> 00:04:28,001
I've always hated you➡

61
00:04:28,001 --> 00:04:31,001
Is there some reason?

62
00:04:33,006 --> 00:04:35,008
reason…?

63
00:04:35,008 --> 00:04:36,508
(sound of door opening)

64
00:04:37,510 --> 00:04:40,513
What are you doing to Koharu-san? Yuio!!

65
00:04:40,513 --> 00:04:43,516
Kurosaki-san, calm down! Please don't stop.

66
00:04:43,516 --> 00:04:46,019
I simply cannot forgive him for targeting Koharu-san.

67
00:04:46,019 --> 00:04:50,023
I... I'm fine, and Yuio-san also apologized.

68
00:04:50,023 --> 00:04:53,026
So please let go.

69
00:04:53,026 --> 00:04:55,026
Koharu-chan...

70
00:05:00,533 --> 00:05:03,933
If Koharu-san says so.

71
00:05:06,973 --> 00:05:10,476
But why did you do this?

72
00:05:10,476 --> 00:05:12,976
Please tell me all the reasons.

73
00:05:15,982 --> 00:05:36,002
♬～

74
00:05:36,002 --> 00:05:56,022
♬～

75
00:05:56,022 --> 00:06:10,970
♬～

76
00:06:10,970 --> 00:06:16,470
♬～

77
00:06:20,980 --> 00:06:26,486
I... I've always hated you.

78
00:06:26,486 --> 00:06:29,489
Even though you are inferior to me in everything➡

79
00:06:29,489 --> 00:06:33,993
As soon as I left home, I was hailed as a genius writer➡

80
00:06:33,993 --> 00:06:37,997
He was so excited about making a public confession at the award ceremony.

81
00:06:37,997 --> 00:06:40,500
Happy you➡

82
00:06:40,500 --> 00:06:44,003
I wanted to make you unhappy.

83
00:06:44,003 --> 00:06:46,503
I don't understand.

84
00:06:49,008 --> 00:06:51,511
You are better than me➡

85
00:06:51,511 --> 00:06:54,511
It's recognized by everyone, right?

86
00:06:55,515 --> 00:06:58,518
I am unnecessary to you➡

87
00:06:58,518 --> 00:07:01,020
It's not worth hating.

88
00:07:01,020 --> 00:07:04,457
Have you forgotten what you did?

89
00:07:04,457 --> 00:07:07,957
You said that to me, who was always clinging to me!

90
00:07:09,462 --> 00:07:12,962
Don't think of me as your brother anymore.

91
00:07:14,467 --> 00:07:18,471
Suddenly he rejected me and left me.

92
00:07:18,471 --> 00:07:21,471
That's the beginning!

93
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:30,983
(薊)((Okay? I wish I could get along with a girl like you➡

94
00:07:30,983 --> 00:07:34,487
Even Yuio becomes a bad girl))

95
00:07:34,487 --> 00:07:37,490
((Please stay away from that girl))

96
00:07:37,490 --> 00:07:40,493
((That's for that child))

97
00:07:40,493 --> 00:07:46,499
♬～

98
00:07:46,499 --> 00:07:48,501
♬～That’s…｡

99
00:07:48,501 --> 00:08:03,901
♬～

100
00:08:06,953 --> 00:08:09,455
Wei Yangjun.

101
00:08:09,455 --> 00:08:12,458
I'm sorry.

102
00:08:12,458 --> 00:08:14,961
Me at that time➡

103
00:08:14,961 --> 00:08:18,965
I thought I shouldn't be near you.

104
00:08:18,965 --> 00:08:21,968
In that house...

105
00:08:21,968 --> 00:08:26,968
Because I'm a nuisance to my family.

106
00:08:28,975 --> 00:08:32,975
The truth is, I didn't want to leave you either.

107
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:38,480
He's the cute little brother I got.

108
00:08:41,487 --> 00:08:47,487
I love Yuo-kun, both in the past and now.

109
00:08:50,997 --> 00:08:53,997
What is it? I love you.

110
00:08:57,003 --> 00:08:59,505
Then…➡

111
00:08:59,505 --> 00:09:04,443
It would be me if you didn't leave me and were my brother.

112
00:09:04,443 --> 00:09:06,946
Because I was weak.

113
00:09:06,946 --> 00:09:10,946
That's right, it's my brother's fault!

114
00:09:12,451 --> 00:09:15,451
I really hate you!

115
00:09:17,456 --> 00:09:22,456
You really don't hate me even now, do you?

116
00:09:23,963 --> 00:09:29,468
Even though we cared about each other, we had gotten past each other.

117
00:09:29,468 --> 00:09:34,473
Again, you said something like you understood.

118
00:09:34,473 --> 00:09:36,473
I... I'm sorry.

119
00:09:37,977 --> 00:09:39,979
Wei Yangjun.

120
00:09:39,979 --> 00:09:44,483
I hurt you because of my thoughts.

121
00:09:44,483 --> 00:09:46,983
I apologize again.

122
00:09:51,490 --> 00:09:54,493
If it continues to be in your life➡

123
00:09:54,493 --> 00:09:57,993
If you'll allow me to get involved...

124
00:10:02,501 --> 00:10:06,501
From now on, I want to face you straight.

125
00:10:09,508 --> 00:10:13,012
Please again...➡

126
00:10:13,012 --> 00:10:15,512
Please be my brother.

127
00:10:21,520 --> 00:10:23,520
Do whatever you want.

128
00:10:26,525 --> 00:10:30,029
Yes, I'll do as I please.

129
00:10:30,029 --> 00:10:33,032
Well then, even though I'm presumptuous, I'd like to start as an older brother➡

130
00:10:33,032 --> 00:10:36,032
There's something I have to do.

131
00:10:42,041 --> 00:10:43,542
Here it goes!

132
00:10:43,542 --> 00:10:47,046
I will now settle the matter that involved Mr. Koharu.

133
00:10:47,046 --> 00:10:50,546
Yuio-kun, if you want to hit me too, please come at me.

134
00:10:53,052 --> 00:10:56,552
This… stupid power!

135
00:10:59,558 --> 00:11:02,995
Eh...it doesn't hurt.

136
00:11:02,995 --> 00:11:05,395
I've never hit anyone.

137
00:11:08,501 --> 00:11:11,003
Now, after the fight, it's time for a hug!

138
00:11:11,003 --> 00:11:13,005
picture? Look!

139
00:11:13,005 --> 00:11:15,508
What are you doing? Wait. Yuio-kun!

140
00:11:15,508 --> 00:11:17,508
what? Stop it!

141
00:11:19,011 --> 00:11:21,514
Koharu-chan

142
00:11:21,514 --> 00:11:24,517
I'm quitting my job as a tutor and my part-time job at the store.

143
00:11:24,517 --> 00:11:26,018
picture?

144
00:11:26,018 --> 00:11:30,022
If you need someone, I'll introduce you.

145
00:11:30,022 --> 00:11:33,025
I'm quite busy.

146
00:11:33,025 --> 00:11:34,527
Yuio-san...

147
00:11:34,527 --> 00:11:37,530
Ah... then let's eat some cake together.

148
00:11:37,530 --> 00:11:40,530
Well, I'll go watch a movie too.

149
00:11:41,534 --> 00:11:44,537
Wei Yangjun.

150
00:11:44,537 --> 00:11:48,537
I'll leave some cake for Yuio-kun too.

151
00:11:52,044 --> 00:11:55,544
I'm a chocolate guy.

152
00:11:59,051 --> 00:12:00,553
yes.

153
00:12:00,553 --> 00:12:12,498
♬～

154
00:12:12,498 --> 00:12:20,498
Smartphone) (vibrating sound)

155
00:12:22,007 --> 00:12:24,510
Mother?

156
00:12:24,510 --> 00:12:27,012
Smartphone) (Ai) Yuio I was thinking about your mother➡

157
00:12:27,012 --> 00:12:30,516
I think it would be better for you to live in a student dormitory.

158
00:12:30,516 --> 00:12:33,018
Smartphone) If I'm with that girl, I'll be ruined...

159
00:12:33,018 --> 00:12:35,521
I'll continue to live with my brother.

160
00:12:35,521 --> 00:12:37,022
Smartphone) Huh?

161
00:12:37,022 --> 00:12:40,022
Well, I don't know when I'll be kicked out.

162
00:12:43,529 --> 00:12:45,531
At best, be happy.

163
00:12:45,531 --> 00:12:47,031
Stupid brother.

164
00:12:55,041 --> 00:12:57,544
Koharu-san, you really haven't done anything, right?

165
00:12:57,544 --> 00:13:00,046
There's not a single scratch on it, right?

166
00:13:00,046 --> 00:13:02,549
It's really nothing.

167
00:13:02,549 --> 00:13:04,551
Ah...｡

168
00:13:04,551 --> 00:13:06,551
good.

169
00:13:09,055 --> 00:13:14,060
I'm sorry for getting you involved in our conflict.

170
00:13:14,060 --> 00:13:16,563
But thanks to Koharu-san➡

171
00:13:16,563 --> 00:13:20,063
We were able to return to our families.

172
00:13:24,070 --> 00:13:26,573
Mr. Koharu.

173
00:13:26,573 --> 00:13:31,077
Would you like to live here with us after you graduate from high school?

174
00:13:31,077 --> 00:13:32,579
picture?

175
00:13:32,579 --> 00:13:35,479
It's still so early...

176
00:13:37,016 --> 00:13:40,520
I have no intention of rushing you or forcing you.

177
00:13:40,520 --> 00:13:46,020
But I... I want to be a family with Koharu-san.

178
00:13:47,527 --> 00:13:51,030
Please take this as a proposal.

179
00:13:51,030 --> 00:13:55,535
Ah...but I don't want to be separated from my family.

180
00:13:55,535 --> 00:13:59,035
If so, you and your family could live here...

181
00:14:06,045 --> 00:14:08,047
《No...》

182
00:14:08,047 --> 00:14:13,047
"I can't concentrate at all because I'm thinking too much..."

183
00:14:14,554 --> 00:14:17,054
After graduating...

184
00:14:20,560 --> 00:14:26,065
《I want to learn cooking and management in order to take over the restaurant》

185
00:14:26,065 --> 00:14:29,565
``But going to higher education costs money.''

186
00:14:33,072 --> 00:14:36,972
Mom, what should I do?

187
00:14:40,513 --> 00:14:43,516
(Kiriya) Did you propose again without hesitation?

188
00:14:43,516 --> 00:14:47,520
Everything I've always wanted has come true.

189
00:14:47,520 --> 00:14:50,023
But unlike before➡

190
00:14:50,023 --> 00:14:53,523
I think we've made progress because we weren't rejected right away.

191
00:14:57,030 --> 00:15:02,535
I understand that you want a family.

192
00:15:02,535 --> 00:15:04,537
But ➡

193
00:15:04,537 --> 00:15:09,042
If you don't want to be a burden to her, please withdraw as soon as possible.

194
00:15:09,042 --> 00:15:11,044
Is it a burden?

195
00:15:11,044 --> 00:15:14,547
This is an important time for Shirase-san as he prepares to enter higher education.

196
00:15:14,547 --> 00:15:18,551
Make her future possibilities with your wishes➡

197
00:15:18,551 --> 00:15:21,051
What will you do if it gets crushed?

198
00:15:23,056 --> 00:15:28,561
Besides, she's the mother in that house, right?

199
00:15:28,561 --> 00:15:37,504
♬～

200
00:15:37,504 --> 00:15:40,507
(Mika) I think it's a wonderful thing, but...

201
00:15:40,507 --> 00:15:44,007
(Riri) Even if you propose to me now.

202
00:15:46,513 --> 00:15:49,015
(Mika) We, Koharu, are the Kurosaki brothers➡

203
00:15:49,015 --> 00:15:53,019
I was so happy when I heard that I was going to be a private tutor.

204
00:15:53,019 --> 00:15:56,022
(Riri) That's right, Koharu loves cooking so much.

205
00:15:56,022 --> 00:15:59,526
I thought you wanted to study more.

206
00:15:59,526 --> 00:16:03,530
But I take care of my shop and my family➡

207
00:16:03,530 --> 00:16:06,533
I also liked Koharu.

208
00:16:06,533 --> 00:16:10,033
(Riri) I think it's wrong for us to speak out.

209
00:16:13,039 --> 00:16:15,041
thank you.

210
00:16:15,041 --> 00:16:18,044
Try to think about what you want to do.

211
00:16:18,044 --> 00:16:21,047
Doesn't Koharu look pale?

212
00:16:21,047 --> 00:16:23,049
Huh? Really? That's bad, right?

213
00:16:23,049 --> 00:16:25,552
Maybe I'm a little sleep deprived. (Riri: Mika) Eh!

214
00:16:25,552 --> 00:16:29,052
(Mika) Hey, you see, lack of sleep is the enemy of beauty!

215
00:16:35,560 --> 00:16:39,060
《Kurosaki-san, are you coming today? 》

216
00:16:40,565 --> 00:16:44,069
《I want to think about the future one by one➡

217
00:16:44,069 --> 00:16:47,069
It's better to talk properly》

218
00:16:50,075 --> 00:16:52,075
《It's a bit hot...》

219
00:16:53,511 --> 00:16:55,013
Ah, Chi-chan, welcome back.

220
00:16:55,013 --> 00:16:57,013
(Chifuyu) I'm home.

221
00:16:59,517 --> 00:17:03,021
Hey, Yuio-san, aren't you coming back?

222
00:17:03,021 --> 00:17:04,522
Ah... yeah.

223
00:17:04,522 --> 00:17:07,525
Yuio-san is busy studying.

224
00:17:07,525 --> 00:17:10,028
Isn't it his fault?

225
00:17:10,028 --> 00:17:13,528
No, it's not Kurosaki-san's fault...

226
00:17:16,034 --> 00:17:19,037
Sister! Sister!

227
00:17:19,037 --> 00:17:21,539
Sister!

228
00:17:21,539 --> 00:17:25,539
⚟Koharu Koharu⚞

229
00:17:31,549 --> 00:17:33,549
((mother…))

230
00:17:35,053 --> 00:17:38,056
(Four seasons)((Looks like you can eat porridge?))

231
00:17:38,056 --> 00:17:44,556
((Hooray, mom's special eggs are boiled with lots of love))

232
00:17:48,066 --> 00:17:49,567
((Good…))

233
00:17:49,567 --> 00:17:51,567
((I'll enjoy having this))

234
00:17:56,508 --> 00:17:58,008
((hehe…))

235
00:18:00,512 --> 00:18:05,512
((Take a good rest and get well soon))

236
00:18:07,018 --> 00:18:10,522
((Ah...sorry, I have to go now))

237
00:18:10,522 --> 00:18:13,024
((Eh... wait))

238
00:18:13,024 --> 00:18:15,026
((Wait mom))

239
00:18:15,026 --> 00:18:17,028
((I'll help you properly))

240
00:18:17,028 --> 00:18:19,030
((Because I don't go out to play))

241
00:18:19,030 --> 00:18:21,030
((Don't go!))

242
00:18:23,034 --> 00:18:25,034
((Don't go...))

243
00:18:32,544 --> 00:18:34,546
Mr. Kurosaki...

244
00:18:34,546 --> 00:18:38,046
Yes, it's me, Koharu-san.

245
00:18:40,552 --> 00:18:43,054
Huh? my room...

246
00:18:43,054 --> 00:18:45,557
Ah, don't overdo it.

247
00:18:45,557 --> 00:18:51,062
Huh? Why is Kurosaki-san in my room...?

248
00:18:51,062 --> 00:18:53,498
(Chifuyu) I informed him.

249
00:18:53,498 --> 00:18:54,999
Chi-chan.

250
00:18:54,999 --> 00:18:59,499
When I told him that I had collapsed at the store, he immediately rushed over.

251
00:19:01,005 --> 00:19:03,508
Careers, stores, etc.➡

252
00:19:03,508 --> 00:19:07,512
You must have gotten a fever thinking about us.

253
00:19:07,512 --> 00:19:11,015
Stop carrying this all by yourself.

254
00:19:11,015 --> 00:19:12,517
picture?

255
00:19:12,517 --> 00:19:14,519
I’m telling you, it’s me➡

256
00:19:14,519 --> 00:19:17,021
I’ll help out at the store instead of my sister➡

257
00:19:17,021 --> 00:19:21,021
I can make dinner and I don't rely on the family money.

258
00:19:24,028 --> 00:19:26,030
Yeah.

259
00:19:26,030 --> 00:19:30,030
Yeah, I see.

260
00:19:31,035 --> 00:19:33,538
Come to the kitchen.

261
00:19:33,538 --> 00:19:37,538
Ku… Mr. Kurosaki.

262
00:19:39,544 --> 00:19:41,544
yes.

263
00:19:43,047 --> 00:19:47,051
Thank you for contacting us.

264
00:19:47,051 --> 00:19:52,056
Because we can't whine about it, sister.

265
00:19:52,056 --> 00:19:53,491
picture?

266
00:19:53,491 --> 00:19:57,491
Have you heard about my mother?

267
00:19:59,497 --> 00:20:01,997
That he passed away.

268
00:20:03,501 --> 00:20:06,004
My mother collapsed at the store➡

269
00:20:06,004 --> 00:20:09,507
Normally, it was time for my sister to help me.

270
00:20:09,507 --> 00:20:14,012
But that day I happened to go out to play➡

271
00:20:14,012 --> 00:20:18,516
Mom, I was alone at the store➡

272
00:20:18,516 --> 00:20:21,019
I noticed it too late...

273
00:20:21,019 --> 00:20:24,022
Sister, there's nothing wrong with you➡

274
00:20:24,022 --> 00:20:27,525
I thought it was my fault.

275
00:20:27,525 --> 00:20:33,531
That's why I don't like Kurosaki-san➡

276
00:20:33,531 --> 00:20:38,531
My sister looks like she's having fun, so I hope it'll be easier.

277
00:20:40,538 --> 00:20:42,540
Chifuyu-san➡

278
00:20:42,540 --> 00:20:46,040
I really love your sister.

279
00:20:48,546 --> 00:20:53,446
I don't want to lose my family anymore...

280
00:20:54,986 --> 00:20:59,490
(sound of cutting vegetables)

281
00:20:59,490 --> 00:21:02,493
⚟Koharu-san enters⚞

282
00:21:02,493 --> 00:21:11,002
♬～

283
00:21:11,002 --> 00:21:13,004
Thank you for waiting.

284
00:21:13,004 --> 00:21:15,004
thank you.

285
00:21:16,507 --> 00:21:18,509
I'll enjoy having this.

286
00:21:18,509 --> 00:21:26,017
♬～

287
00:21:26,017 --> 00:21:29,020
Handmade by Chifuyu.

288
00:21:29,020 --> 00:21:32,020
It's very delicious.

289
00:21:35,526 --> 00:21:41,032
Koharu-san, have you been worried about your career path?

290
00:21:41,032 --> 00:21:44,035
Ah... yes.

291
00:21:44,035 --> 00:21:48,039
Sorry, I couldn't notice anything.

292
00:21:48,039 --> 00:21:51,542
No, it's my fault.

293
00:21:51,542 --> 00:21:56,981
I don't know what to do.

294
00:21:56,981 --> 00:21:58,483
Hehe...

295
00:21:58,483 --> 00:22:04,489
♬～

296
00:22:04,489 --> 00:22:06,489
Mr. Koharu.

297
00:22:08,493 --> 00:22:13,993
Please forget about the proposal the other day.

298
00:22:15,500 --> 00:22:17,001
picture?

299
00:22:17,001 --> 00:22:21,005
You don't have to think about me right now.

300
00:22:21,005 --> 00:22:24,008
It wasn't Kurosaki-san's fault that he collapsed, right?

301
00:22:24,008 --> 00:22:26,511
No, it's my fault.

302
00:22:26,511 --> 00:22:30,014
I'm only thinking about myself.

303
00:22:30,014 --> 00:22:35,014
Everything about wanting to live together was forced on me unilaterally.

304
00:22:36,521 --> 00:22:39,023
sorry.

305
00:22:39,023 --> 00:22:43,027
I will refrain from going to the store for a while.

306
00:22:43,027 --> 00:22:45,530
Please excuse me today.

307
00:22:45,530 --> 00:22:48,530
Please take care.

308
00:22:50,034 --> 00:22:53,971
Ah... oh wait, Kurosaki-san...

309
00:22:53,971 --> 00:23:00,978
♬～

310
00:23:00,978 --> 00:23:02,978
(sound of door closing)

311
00:23:05,483 --> 00:23:09,983
Kurosaki-san, why...?
